title: Bills Titans Recap & Arif Hasan on the Vikings
itunes:title: Bills Titans Recap & Arif Hasan on the Vikings
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal & Marc Sessler recap the crazy Monday Night Football game between the Buffalo Bills and the Tennessee Titans. Arif Hasan joins to talk where the Vikings sit during their bye week and the heroes preview the TNF matchup between the Broncos and Browns.
